      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This chassis has been proactively maintained, with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term reliability. The 6-speed manual transmission shifts with tactile precision, paired with a refreshed Sachs clutch and a factory limited-slip differential. Performance is enhanced by Bilstein dampers and a cooling system refresh",
